arm_group.description:
Cohort 1 will receive standard of care concomitantly with1000 mg/day of MBM-02.
Patients will receive standard of care treatment for newly diagnosed Glioblastoma multiforme consisting of four sequential periods:
1 week run-in with MBM-02 prior to radiotherapy;
6 weeks of radiotherapy and concomitant temozolomide;
4 weeks of rest post-radiotherapy and concomitant temozolomide; and
Adjuvant temozolomide treatment post 4-week rest period. Patients will be administered daily MBM-02 during all four sequential periods.

Cohort 2 will receive standard of care concomitantly with1200 mg/day of MBM-02.
Patients will receive standard of care treatment for newly diagnosed Glioblastoma multiforme consisting of four sequential periods:
1 week run-in with MBM-02 prior to radiotherapy;
